DialogueDictionary.RSS_EARTH_HEA_CAMPSITE_RECORDER_PAGE_1: So for starters I have no idea how I ended up here.
DialogueDictionary.RSS_EARTH_HEA_CAMPSITE_RECORDER_PAGE_2: I'm also not entirely sure where exactly here is.
DialogueDictionary.RSS_EARTH_HEA_CAMPSITE_RECORDER_PAGE_3: Seems I'm not the only one who's been here, judging by the Nomai ruins nearby.
DialogueDictionary.RSS_EARTH_HEA_CAMPSITE_RECORDER_PAGE_4: I'll go check those out tomorrow, for now I think I deserve a little rest.
DialogueDictionary.RSS_EARTH_NOM_RAFT_RECORDER_PAGE_1: Allium: This raft was here when we arrived.
DialogueDictionary.RSS_EARTH_NOM_RAFT_RECORDER_PAGE_2: Allium: Hypothesis 1: It was left here by the original inhabitants of this planet.
DialogueDictionary.RSS_EARTH_NOM_RAFT_RECORDER_PAGE_3: Allium: Hypothesis 2: We are not the only ones to have been marooned here.
DialogueDictionary.RSS_EARTH_NOM_RAFT_RECORDER_PAGE_4: Musa: Unrelated hypothesis, this raft would have made our ocean crossing much easier.
DialogueDictionary.RSS_EARTH_NOM_RAFT_RECORDER_PAGE_5: Allium: I believe that is more of an objective fact than a theory, Musa.
